{
  "stem": "2373.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For three days, we didn't wash and didn't do-- so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after the shower, then we were sent to the next room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There we were shaven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our hair was shaven off, also under the arm, under-- the pubic hair, everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From there, we went to the next room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There, we got our clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody got something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No underwear, only one-- one something-- regardless how big you are, how small you are, what size you are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I got a dark brown see-through summer frock without underwear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was long to my ankle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when my friend, my best friend saw me, she said, god, Martha.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are ugly, I mean, [LAUGHS] without hair in that outfit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So then we walked again, and walked, and walked until we came on-- in-- in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, when we arrived at the gate, there was a music, an orchestra-- a woman's orchestra in striped-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were the [NON-ENGLISH], the prisoner's orchestra.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was a big gate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was written arbeit macht frei.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Work makes you free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we thought we will work, we will do something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But in all, anyhow, that wasn't like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived, finally, to a big barrack which was all empty, no beds, no bunks, no straw, nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was for about 500 or 800 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were pushed in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was, again, so crammed that we couldn't-- couldn't-- not everybody could stretch out lying down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, that's where we spent about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] five, six weeks doing absolutely, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the barracks, we were only at night til the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the day, it wasn't allowed to enter that barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, I've never seen-- we couldn't work it out where we are.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
